{"reponsecode": 0, "reponsemessage": "", "data": {"exhibit_id": "ahbwysjy_museum_xgdx_bvlz", "exhibition_name": "安徽文明史陈列（一）", "location": "0,0", "name": "金边玛瑙碗", "size": "", "like": 0, "share_url": "mob/exhibit/detail?exhibit_id=3413", "is_favorited": 0, "_3d_url": "museum/show3d.php?fileroot=ahbwysjy_museum&exhibit_id=3413&scale=0.5", "description": "金边玛瑙碗是安徽省目前惟一一件玉器类“国宝级”文物。整个碗呈橙黄色，局部有暗红色斑块，采用我国北方特有的火玛瑙制成。碗壁较薄，于半透明地朦胧中显露出玛瑙的自然纹理和柔和光泽。碗口沿着边缘了镶一圈金边，宋代的官宦阶层和富裕人家，往往喜欢在器物的口沿上包镶金边，这种锦上添花的包镶技术，更增加了器物的富丽和华贵。", "images": ["content/fileroot/museum/ahbwysjy_museum/image/e33vyDvfa0_s.webp", "content/fileroot/museum/ahbwysjy_museum/image/nNuRJQvWlJ_s.webp"], "audio": [{"audiotype": "mandarin", "filename": "content/fileroot/museum/ahbwysjy_museum/audio/OvavRgt2Cr.mp3"}], "video": {"videourl": "", "img": ""}, "ispaid": 1}}